esent, however, accretion in two funnel\nstreams dominates if Theta > 15 degrees. The results of these simulations can\nbe applied to accreting magnetized stars with relatively small magnetospheres:\nClassical T Tauri stars, accreting millisecond X-ray pulsars, and cataclysmics\nvariables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 20:25:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 May 2016 22:39:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-18"}
