centricities. The main\nthreat to newly born triple systems is internal instabilities, not external\nperturbations. Dynamical interactions in newborn triple systems of stellar\nembryos embedded in and accreting from a cloud core naturally form a population\nof freefloating BD binaries, and this mechanism may constitute a significant\npathway for the formation of BD binaries. (Abstract abbreviated).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jan 2015 00:05:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
