mbedded. These results shed some light to\nthe origin of nonlinearities in voids, going beyond the fact that voids just\nquickly becomes nonlinear as they become emptier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jan 2015 12:17:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-30"}
